{"word":"水","reading":"みず","meaning":"water","pos":"noun","example":"水をください。","exampleReading":"みずをください。","exampleMeaning":"Water, please.","tip":"Cold water only — hot water is お湯 (oyu). Ask for 水 in a restaurant and it comes iced.","pitch":0},
