{"word":"来る","reading":"くる","meaning":"to come","pos":"verb","example":"友だちが来る。","exampleReading":"ともだちがくる。","exampleMeaning":"A friend is coming.","tip":"One of only two irregular verbs: 来る→来ます (きます)→来ない (こない). The reading changes!","pitch":1},
{"word":"見る","reading":"みる","meaning":"to see, to watch","pos":"verb","example":"映画を見る。","exampleReading":"えいがをみる。","exampleMeaning":"I watch a movie.","tip":"Watching TV, seeing a movie, looking at anything — all 見る.","pitch":1},
